      "author": "Delino-WKB",
      "description": "## 🚀 What's New in v0.0.4\r\n### ✨ Toolbar Enhancements\r\n- **Document Title Badge**: Added a clean, styled file name badge at the far-left of the PDF toolbar for instant document identification.\r\n- **Collapse / Expand Button**: Added a new toggle button (`chevron-up` / `chevron-down`) in the PDF toolbar to fold/collapse the PDF container, keeping only the top toolbar visible.\r\n- **Overlap & Toolbar Fixes**: Prevented custom toolbar buttons from overlapping with Obsidian's native `</>` embed edit button, ensuring clean layout across mobile and desktop.\r\n### 🔍 Settings Preview\r\n- **Open Preview in New Tab**: Clicking \"Preview\" in the plugin settings now opens the selected PDF directly in a new native Obsidian tab for full-featured viewing, zooming, and page navigation.",
